00:16:01,812 --> 00:16:03,729
Just let them progress.

384
00:16:08,135 --> 00:16:09,135
There we go.

385
00:16:13,941 --> 00:16:14,903
There.

386
00:16:14,903 --> 00:16:17,570
Look at all them little rascals.

387
00:16:19,861 --> 00:16:21,346
Okay.

388
00:16:21,346 --> 00:16:23,894
With a knife here, I'm
just using the point,

