00:16:41,525 --> 00:16:44,815
And we'll drop a bigger tree in here.

398
00:16:44,816 --> 00:16:46,699
There he goes.

399
00:16:46,698 --> 00:16:47,698
There he is.

400
00:16:50,312 --> 00:16:51,818
There.

401
00:16:51,818 --> 00:16:53,091
These little trees live in your fan brush,

402
00:16:53,091 --> 00:16:56,423
and you have to scare them out sometime.

403
00:16:57,567 --> 00:16:58,400
There.

404
00:17:00,629 --> 00:17:02,557
See, I knew you could do it.

405
00:17:02,557 --> 00:17:05,339
(bristling)

406
00:17:05,339 --> 00:17:08,091
Just let that come right on down.

407
00:17:08,092 --> 00:17:09,884
Maybe there's some trees on
the other side over here too.

