00:17:15,422 --> 00:17:17,243
we might as well just
keep going with them.

411
00:17:17,243 --> 00:17:19,576
(bristling)

412
00:17:26,954 --> 00:17:27,788
Okay.

413
00:17:27,788 --> 00:17:28,621
And by now, you're probably saying,

414
00:17:28,621 --> 00:17:30,456
"Hey, can he do anything but evergreens?"

415
00:17:30,455 --> 00:17:33,902
Alright, let's do some
different types of trees.

