00:19:53,959 --> 00:19:54,792
Alright.

464
00:19:56,445 --> 00:19:57,820
Maybe a little something underneath here,

465
00:19:57,820 --> 00:20:01,178
just to give it a little more depth.

466
00:20:01,179 --> 00:20:02,179
There we go.

467
00:20:05,426 --> 00:20:06,905
Now, we'll cut a few more

