00:20:33,755 --> 00:20:35,570
"I'd buy that painting from you."

482
00:20:35,569 --> 00:20:38,096
So I told him, I said, "You
start writing the check,

483
00:20:38,096 --> 00:20:39,375
"and by the time the check's done,

484
00:20:39,375 --> 00:20:40,783
"you'll have a little pond."

485
00:20:40,784 --> 00:20:43,071
So, watch right here,
let's see what happens.

